            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Wesleyan Female Institute</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <transcript>
                    <p>We are requested to state that the Rev. Jas. A. McCauley, of Fredericksburg, will deliver a 
                        baccalaureate address before the graduating class of the Wesleyan Female Institute, at the 
                        Baptist Church, Staunton, on Sunday next, at 11 o'clock;  and that the Rev. B. F. Brooke, of 
                        Baltimore, will deliver a literary address before the School, at the same place, on Wednesday 
                        night, the 29th inst.  The public are invited to attend.
                    </p>
                </transcript>
