                        <pf>Mr.</pf>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Van</ln>
                        <fn>Robert Albert</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Van</ln>
                        <fn>Theodore Lewis</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf/>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Van lost his two sons on Plum Street when they jumped from a dray for fun.</summary>
                <note>aubrowser/rvjune59.html#6.24e</note>
            </div>
